The code chunk implements a toggle functionality to pause or resume a motion trail animation. When paused, the animation's progress is frozen and resumes from the same point when unpaused. The implementation adjusts internal timing variables to ensure smooth continuation of the animation after resuming.

if self.fade:
                self.fade_start_time += delta_time

            self.pause = False

    def toggle_pause_motion_trail(self, current_time):
        if self.pause:
            self.resume_motion_trail(current_time)
        else:
            self.pause_motion_trail(current_time)
